      &lt;h2 id=&quot;1111-有效括号的嵌套深度&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1111-有效括号的嵌套深度&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1111.有效括号的嵌套深度&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1111.有效括号的嵌套深度&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;:black_nib:解题思路：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;一道看不懂的题…&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;java&quot;&gt;public class Solution &amp;amp;#123;
    public int[] maxDepthAfterSplit(String seq) &amp;amp;#123;
        int[] ans = new int [seq.length()];
        int idx = 0;
        for(char c: seq.toCharArray()) &amp;amp;#123;
            ans[idx++] = c == &#39;(&#39; ? idx &amp;amp; 1 : ((idx + 1) &amp;amp; 1);
        &amp;amp;#125;
        return ans;
    &amp;amp;#125;
&amp;amp;#125;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
